extendedInfo.description: Mobile Banking on Android, provided by Sparebanken MÃ¸re, gives you easy access to the most commonly used banking services. With the bank in your pocket, you can check your balance or pay bills anytime, anywhere â now with new and smart drag-and-drop functions. Account BalanceYou can check the balance of selected accounts and get an overview of the latest transactions. You use the same code as you do in Telebank or SMS Bank to sign in - the four digit code.Mobile BankingIf you want access to more services than balance and recent transactions, you can log into the Mobile Bank. Here you can pay bills, transfer money, pay eFaktura or make changes in the maturity index.With drag-and-drop functions you press your account to access services for the chosen account. If you press and hold for more than one second, you will be able to transfer money to other accounts by sliding the account icon and dropping it on other accounts to which you have access. If you get an eFaktura to process, you can drag and drop it on one of your accounts.To access Mobile Banking, you need a Mobile Banking Agreement which you can find in your Nettbank under "Mine innstillinger" - "MobilBank".To access the Mobile Bank the following is required:-   User name that match your personal identification number-   Telephone or SMS Banking Code (four digits)-   Code from the security device (used by, among other things, to pay bills)Do not have a code?New code can be retrieved in the Nettbank - under the menu "Mine innstillinger" - "MobilBank".Contact UsIf you have any questions please contact Customer Service or your nearestSparebanken MÃ¸re office.For more information about Mobile Banking on Android visit sbm.no.

reviews.title: Gjennomf\303\270rt d\303\245rlig
reviews.comment: Ikoner som gir lite mening og er vanskelig \303\245 treffe. Mye av skjermen brukes til egenreklame og flere operasjoner krever kodebrikke. Dette virker som gammel GUI-tankegang som er tvunget inn i en mobil skjerm. F\303\270lger i tillegg ikke Android spesifikasjonene for grafisk grensesnitt.
reviews.author: Tore Gresdal

reviews.title: Overf\303\270ring av penger til utlandskonto??
reviews.comment: Brukervennlig nok for meg, men den mangler funksjonen hvor jeg kan overf\303\270re penger fra konto til utlandet, hadde den hatt denne muligheten s\303\245 hadde jeg blitt veldig forn\303\270yd.
reviews.author: Frank Robert Nilsen

reviews.title: Fungere som den skal.. MEN
reviews.comment: Appen fungerer utmerket, men grensesnittet er utdatert. Enkle ting som back knappen b\303\270r komme p\303\245 plass. I tillegg til en del lagg og generelt trege l\303\270sninger som b\303\270r ordnes
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Ok
reviews.comment: D\303\245rlig grensesnitt, virker som en halvhjertet iphone port. St\303\270tter ikke ting som back-knappen?! Mangler rablet st\303\270tte
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Knallbra!
reviews.comment: Har savnet en android-app! Synd det ser ut som iOS-app. Fungerer knallbra!
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Appen fungerer som den skal
reviews.comment: Men virker som en billig port fra iOS. Generelle funksjoner som back knappen burde v\303\246rt p\303\245 plass, og optimaliseringer av grensesnittet s\303\245 det ikke virker som alt du gj\303\270r hakker.
reviews.author: A Google User
